    <item>
      <title>法院裁决后芝加哥市长的“豪宅税”重新回到选票上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/chicago-mayor-s-mansion-tax-back-on-ballot-after-court-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊 (Brandon Johnson) 提出的一项颇具争议的措施，即对 100 万美元或以上的房地产交易增税，已正式回到 3 月 19 日的投票中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/chicago-mayor-s-mansion-tax-back-on-ballot-after-court-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:28:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国众议院在政府关门截止日期前批准 4600 亿美元法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/us-house-approves-460-billion-bill-ahead-of-shutdown-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院批准了一项 4600 亿美元的支出法案，并将其送交参议院，预计该法案将及时通过，以避免周六部分政府关门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/us-house-approves-460-billion-bill-ahead-of-shutdown-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:21:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>藤森废除参议院30年后秘鲁将恢复参议院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/peru-to-revive-senate-30-years-after-fujimori-abolished-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁支离破碎的国会形成了绝对多数，以复兴参议院，三十年后，参议院因时任总统阿尔韦托·藤森决定解散整个立法机构而被废除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/peru-to-revive-senate-30-years-after-fujimori-abolished-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:18:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在抛弃共和党竞争对手后鼓励拜登进行辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/trump-challenges-biden-to-debate-after-jilting-republican-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在拒绝与共和党初选对手参加同一论坛后，向乔·拜登总统发起辩论挑战，这一态度转变恰逢 2024 年大选正式开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/trump-challenges-biden-to-debate-after-jilting-republican-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:16:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特通过削减开支和税收来划定选举战线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/hunt-draws-election-battle-lines-with-cuts-to-spending-and-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特在为即将到来的选举划定政治战线时，通过窃取工党的旗舰政策和挤压公共服务，向数百万英国工人提供每年 100 亿英镑（127 亿美元）的减税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/hunt-draws-election-battle-lines-with-cuts-to-spending-and-taxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:35:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰里米·亨特延长儿童福利并誓言改革“不公平”制度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/jeremy-hunt-extends-child-benefit-in-budget-and-vows-to-reform-unfair-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特改变了儿童保育福利开始消失的收入门槛后，近 50 万家庭将能够申请儿童保育福利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/jeremy-hunt-extends-child-benefit-in-budget-and-vows-to-reform-unfair-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:08:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登任命波德斯塔为气候外交官受到共和党调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/biden-s-naming-of-podesta-as-top-climate-diplomat-probed-by-gop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会共和党人正在调查总统乔·拜登任命约翰·波德斯塔取代约翰·克里作为其首席气候外交官的决定，指责白宫在没有经过参议院确认程序的情况下任命他规避法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/biden-s-naming-of-podesta-as-top-climate-diplomat-probed-by-gop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会投票决定为会议城市提供更多安全基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/congress-to-vote-on-raising-security-funds-for-convention-cities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥和密尔沃基是今年夏天民主党和共和党全国代表大会的主办城市，预计将获得总计 1.5 亿美元的联邦资金，用于活动的安保费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/congress-to-vote-on-raising-security-funds-for-convention-cities</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及意外加息，国际货币基金组织释放 80 亿美元贷款以缓解危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-gets-breakthrough-imf-deal-to-lift-loan-size-to-8-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及和国际货币基金组织同意将该国的救助计划增加一倍多，达到 80 亿美元，这是近期全球为稳定因战争和通货膨胀而资金短缺的地区关键国家所做努力的顶峰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-gets-breakthrough-imf-deal-to-lift-loan-size-to-8-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 14:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
